{"ja480:0.1":"Jataka ","ja480:0.2":"Terasakanipata ","ja480:0.3":"Ambavagga ","ja480:0.4":"7. Akittijataka ","ja480:1.1":"“Akittim disva sammantam, ","ja480:1.2":"sakko bhutapati bravi; ","ja480:1.3":"Kim patthayam mahabrahme, ","ja480:1.4":"eko sammasi ghammani”. ","ja480:2.1":"“Dukkho punabbhavo sakka, ","ja480:2.2":"sarirassa ca bhedanam; ","ja480:2.3":"Sammohamaranam dukkham, ","ja480:2.4":"tasma sammami vasava”. ","ja480:3.1":"“Etasmim te sulapite, ","ja480:3.2":"patirupe subhasite; ","ja480:3.3":"Varam kassapa te dammi, ","ja480:3.4":"yam kinci manasicchasi”. ","ja480:4.1":"“Varance me ado sakka, ","ja480:4.2":"sabbabhutanamissara; ","ja480:4.3":"Yena putte ca dare ca, ","ja480:4.4":"dhanadhannam piyani ca; ","ja480:4.5":"Laddha nara na tappanti, ","ja480:4.6":"so lobho na mayi vase”. ","ja480:5.1":"“Etasmim te sulapite, ","ja480:5.2":"patirupe subhasite; ","ja480:5.3":"Varam kassapa te dammi, ","ja480:5.4":"yam kinci manasicchasi”. ","ja480:6.1":"“Varance me ado sakka, ","ja480:6.2":"sabbabhutanamissara; ","ja480:6.3":"Khettam vatthum hirannanca, ","ja480:6.4":"gavassam dasaporisam; ","ja480:6.5":"Yena jatena jiyanti, ","ja480:6.6":"so doso na mayi vase”. ","ja480:7.1":"“Etasmim te sulapite, ","ja480:7.2":"patirupe subhasite; ","ja480:7.3":"Varam kassapa te dammi, ","ja480:7.4":"yam kinci manasicchasi”. ","ja480:8.1":"“Varance me ado sakka, ","ja480:8.2":"sabbabhutanamissara; ","ja480:8.3":"Balam na passe na sune, ","ja480:8.4":"na ca balena samvase; ","ja480:8.5":"Balenallapasallapam, ","ja480:8.6":"na kare na ca rocaye”. ","ja480:9.1":"“Kim nu te akaram balo, ","ja480:9.2":"vada kassapa karanam; ","ja480:9.3":"Kena kassapa balassa, ","ja480:9.4":"dassanam nabhikankhasi”. ","ja480:10.1":"“Anayam nayati dummedho, ","ja480:10.2":"adhurayam niyunjati; ","ja480:10.3":"Dunnayo seyyaso hoti, ","ja480:10.4":"samma vutto pakuppati; ","ja480:10.5":"Vinayam so na janati, ","ja480:10.6":"sadhu tassa adassanam”. ","ja480:11.1":"“Etasmim te sulapite, ","ja480:11.2":"patirupe subhasite; ","ja480:11.3":"Varam kassapa te dammi, ","ja480:11.4":"yam kinci manasicchasi”. ","ja480:12.1":"“Varance me ado sakka, ","ja480:12.2":"sabbabhutanamissara; ","ja480:12.3":"Dhiram passe sune dhiram, ","ja480:12.4":"dhirena saha samvase; ","ja480:12.5":"Dhirenallapasallapam, ","ja480:12.6":"tam kare tanca rocaye”. ","ja480:13.1":"“Kim nu te akaram dhiro, ","ja480:13.2":"vada kassapa karanam; ","ja480:13.3":"Kena kassapa dhirassa, ","ja480:13.4":"dassanam abhikankhasi”. ","ja480:14.1":"“Nayam nayati medhavi, ","ja480:14.2":"adhurayam na yunjati; ","ja480:14.3":"Sunayo seyyaso hoti, ","ja480:14.4":"samma vutto na kuppati; ","ja480:14.5":"Vinayam so pajanati, ","ja480:14.6":"sadhu tena samagamo”. ","ja480:15.1":"“Etasmim te sulapite, ","ja480:15.2":"patirupe subhasite; ","ja480:15.3":"Varam kassapa te dammi, ","ja480:15.4":"yam kinci manasicchasi”. ","ja480:16.1":"“Varance me ado sakka, ","ja480:16.2":"sabbabhutanamissara; ","ja480:16.3":"Tato ratya vivasane, ","ja480:16.4":"suriyuggamanam pati; ","ja480:16.5":"Dibba bhakkha patubhaveyyum, ","ja480:16.6":"silavanto ca yacaka. ","ja480:17.1":"Dadato me na khiyetha, ","ja480:17.2":"datva nanutapeyyaham; ","ja480:17.3":"Dadam cittam pasadeyyam, ","ja480:17.4":"etam sakka varam vare”. ","ja480:18.1":"“Etasmim te sulapite, ","ja480:18.2":"patirupe subhasite; ","ja480:18.3":"Varam kassapa te dammi, ","ja480:18.4":"yam kinci manasicchasi”. ","ja480:19.1":"“Varance me ado sakka, ","ja480:19.2":"sabbabhutanamissara; ","ja480:19.3":"Na mam puna upeyyasi, ","ja480:19.4":"etam sakka varam vare”. ","ja480:20.1":"“Bahuhi vatacariyahi, ","ja480:20.2":"nara ca atha nariyo; ","ja480:20.3":"Dassanam abhikankhanti, ","ja480:20.4":"kim nu me dassane bhayam”. ","ja480:21.1":"“Tam tadisam devavannam, ","ja480:21.2":"sabbakamasamiddhinam; ","ja480:21.3":"Disva tapo pamajjeyyam, ","ja480:21.4":"etam te dassane bhayan”ti. ","ja480:22.1":"Akittijatakam sattamam. "}